OL,3,C'Prolific thief' hides from police
OL,4,Cofficers under bed to avoid arrest
OL,6,FPolice have released a video of a
OL,7,F'prolific thief' who tried to evade
OL,8,Fofficers by hiding under a bed in
OL,9,FFaversham.
OL,11,FBilly Bird of Everland Lane in
OL,12,FOspringe carried out a two-week spree
OL,13,Fof thefts across Faversham and Ashford.
OL,15,FPolice say he targeted multiple
OL,16,Fstores, stealing items including
OL,17,Falcohol and groceries.
