OL,3,C'Prolific thief' hides from police
OL,4,Cofficers under bed to avoid arrest
OL,6,FOn Tuesday 19 August (2025) the 27-
OL,7,Fyear-old entered Tesco in Faversham,
OL,8,Fhid a bottle of whiskey in his hoodie,
OL,9,Fand left without paying.
OL,11,FThat same day, he visited Sainsbury's
OL,12,Fin Bysing Wood Road twice, stealing
OL,13,Falcohol worth nearly #200.
OL,15,FOn Wednesday 27 August (2025), he
OL,16,Fstole groceries worth #75 from the Co-
OL,17,Fop in Hunters Avenue in Ashford, and
OL,18,Freturned later that afternoon to steal
OL,19,Fmore items.
