OL,3,C'Prolific thief' hides from police
OL,4,Cofficers under bed to avoid arrest
OL,6,FThat evening, police say, he went back
OL,7,Fto Tesco in Faversham and stole
OL,8,Falcohol valued at #212.
OL,10,FIn the early hours of the following
OL,11,Fmorning, Bird refuelled his vehicle at
OL,12,Fthe Thanet Way services to the value
OL,13,Fof #80.06 and drove off without making
OL,14,Fany attempt to pay.
OL,16,FOn Thursday 4 September (2025), he
OL,17,Fagain targeted Sainsbury's in
OL,18,FFaversham, stealing three bottles of
OL,19,Fvodka.
