OL,3,C'Prolific thief' hides from police
OL,4,Cofficers under bed to avoid arrest
OL,6,FOfficers arrested Bird the next day at
OL,7,Fa property in Whiting Crescent, where
OL,8,Fhe was found hiding under a bed.
OL,10,FBilly Berd has been jailed for 8 weeks
OL,11,Fand will be banned from entering shops
OL,12,Fin the area for three years following
OL,13,Fhis release from prison.
OL,15,FSergeant Christopher Hill said:
OL,16,F"Bird's repeated thefts caused
OL,17,Fdisruption and loss to several
OL,18,Fbusinesses across Faversham and
OL,19,FAshford.
