OL,6,F"Thanks to the swift work of our
OL,7,Fofficers, he was identified, arrested,
OL,8,Fand brought before the courts.
OL,10,F"The Criminal Behaviour Order imposed
OL,11,Fwill help protect local retailers from
OL,12,Ffurther offending and sends a clear
OL,13,Fmessage that this kind of behaviour
OL,14,Fwill not be tolerated."
